# M6 P07 Phase 4 — jet-pack horizontal verification.
#
# Two scenarios captured in sequence:
#   (a) pure JET (no L/R)        — should rise straight up
#   (b) JET + RIGHT              — should rise up + drift right
#
# Phase 4 adds a horizontal jet component at 50 % of vertical thrust
# magnitude, applied only when BTN_LEFT or BTN_RIGHT is latched. With
# JET_THRUST_PXS2 = 2200 and dt = 1/60:
#   fy = -2200 / 3600 = -0.611 px/tick²   (straight up)
#   fx = +0.5 · |fy| · run_sign           (when L/R held)
#
# Phase 2's air branch in apply_run_velocity caps run-input contribution
# at RUN_SPEED (4.667 px/tick). Phase 4's fx pushes vx past the cap;
# Phase 2's above-cap return then preserves the excess until drag
# (0.99/tick) bleeds it down. Steady-state horizontal speed while
# jetting+RIGHT settles well above RUN_SPEED — the "jet covers
# distance" the user asked for.
#
# Fuel: JET_DRAIN_PER_SEC=0.60, max=1.20, regen ~0.20/s while grounded.
# Scenario (a) drains 25 ticks worth = 0.25 fuel; scenario (b) drains
# another 35 ticks worth = 0.35 fuel. Between them we hold neither
# button and let the mech land + refuel.

window 1920 1080
seed 1 0
out build/shots/m6_movement_jet
spawn_at 800 800
aim 1500 800

# (a) Settle.
at  20 shot settled

# (b) Pure JET — straight up, no horizontal drift.
at  40 press jet
at  50 shot jet_t010
at  60 shot jet_t020
at  65 release jet

# (c) Let the mech fall + land + refuel before scenario (b).
at 100 shot postjet_t035
at 200 shot refueled_t135

# (d) JET + RIGHT — diagonal trajectory (up + right).
at 220 press right
at 220 press jet
at 230 shot jetright_t010
at 240 shot jetright_t020
at 250 shot jetright_t030
at 260 shot jetright_t040
at 265 release jet
at 265 release right

# (e) Capture descent + landing.
at 290 shot descending_t025
at 320 shot landed_t055

contact_sheet jet_sheet cols 4

at 360 end
